<br>
From what I can tell, the human KoS Ragefire spawns in the Northeast corner of Skyfire now.  This, of course, is based on the number of clerics now sitting in that corner <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :lol --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/laugh.gif ALT=":lol"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> .  This human appears to be on a 3 day timer.  When killed, this human changes to dragon form.  Apparently, the two ideas behind this are 1) making the Ragefire and Nagafen spawns completely independant (as stated by Kodylan), and 2) making it so that a cleric won't lose their epic piece by having an opposing force gank the dragon after that cleric turns in their piece, causing them to have to get another pearl and try again. <p><img src="http://home.swbell.net/sdspies/images/caederesig.jpg" BORDER="0" WIDTH="216"
